snippet.title: AUTO FACTORY - Steam Game Trailer
snippet.description:
Available on the Steam market place: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1143170/Auto_Factory/

Auto Factory is the simulation game where you get to build your own automated factory out of a range of different block types. You then use machines to turn materials into products which you can sell to make money.
